title: Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 4 DEMO PS2 Rare
description:
This should be a treat to anyone who still has a soft-modded ps2 or PCSX2, the original THPS4 demo that was packed in the Kelly Slater game before THPS4 came out.

I ripped the demo out of it, rebuilt as an .ISO, tested in PCSX2 and it is fully functional, and in all it's original glory with early textures, logos, etc.

The demo itself includes Practice and College, and the main menu is fully scrollable with nothing blocked out.
